OL,3,CCyclist's own bodycam lands him #1,200
OL,4,Cfine
OL,6,FA cyclist who sent footage to police
OL,7,Fcomplaining about bad driving has been
OL,8,Fordered to pay more than #1,200 in
OL,9,Fcourt costs himself after it revealed
OL,10,Fhis own careless riding.
OL,12,FThe Leeds cyclist uploaded a video to
OL,13,FWest Yorkshire Police showing a car
OL,14,Fpassing too close to his bike in
OL,15,FMenston near Ilkley.
OL,17,FA force spokesperson said: "Later on
OL,18,Fin the same submission, he captured
OL,19,Fhimself riding without due care and
OL,20,Fattention as he approached a parked
OL,21,Fcar and an oncoming vehicle.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
