OL,3,CCyclist's own bodycam lands him #1,200
OL,4,Cfine
OL,6,F"Rather than slow down or have to
OL,7,Funclip from his pedals, the rider
OL,8,Fchose to travel between the parked car
OL,9,Fand the vehicle heading directly
OL,10,Ftowards him."
OL,12,FThe force said the driver was forced
OL,13,Fto "hug the kerb" to avoid a collision.
OL,15,FThe rider was ordered to pay fines and
OL,16,Fcosts of more than #1,200 by Bradford
OL,17,Fmagistrates.
